Autokaggler Notices

This repository contains Autokaggler source code, tests, documentation, and a small synthetic Titanic-shaped sample dataset for offline tests.

No NVIDIA/nvidia-kaggle source code is vendored in this repository. The optional NVIDIA bridge only exposes metadata and an opt-in local command hook for users who separately install or configure compatible tooling.

The files under data/sample are synthetic examples created for repository tests. They are not Kaggle competition data and do not contain real passenger records.

Kaggle API access, downloaded competition data, generated submissions, credentials, logs, caches, and virtual environments should remain local and are excluded by .gitignore.

